rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Did I mention that I'm a botanist
and I've traveled all over Alst?

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0002
rows.name: I can give you a little advice.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0003
rows.name: What do you want to ask about?

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0008
rows.name: Have you heard of the Sirius Anemone?

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0009
rows.name:
It's a flower you don't see often,
but it's easy to collect in the Fons
Maim Waters, below Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0011
rows.name: Do you know about the Amber Leaf?

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0012
rows.name:
Plants themselves are rare in Superbia,
where there's almost no water, but I've
collected some in the Old City of Teddim.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0015
rows.name: I never expected you to ask that...

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0016
rows.name:
I'm afraid even I can't
answer that question...

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0017
rows.name:
That country is isolationist,
so you can't get in without
a very good reason.

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0018
rows.name:
Besides, I don't even know where
its Divine Beast is wandering...

rows.label: tlk41700126_03_msg0019
rows.name:
When you think about it that way, I
guess I still have a lot to learn.
